            <p class="my-3">
                Convrtr began as a set of fast, dependable PHP scripts supporting the Halo ARG community through rapid-fire decoding challenges. Inspired by the loss of tools like Everlost and Xlate, it evolved into a portable microsite and later a lightweight JavaScript app, designed for solvers needing reliable, offline-friendly converters anywhere. Today, Convrtr remains a nimble, always-ready toolkit for anyone tackling encoded text, carrying forward the spirit of the puzzle-solving community.
            </p>
